== Maintaining a MoinMoin wiki ==
The following pages contain information on various subtopics important to Moin``Moin admins.

Regular tasks:
 * HelpOnPageDeletion - how to delete pages
 * HelpOnAccessControlLists - how to manage access to pages
 * HelpOnUserHandling - how to manage user accounts

Installing and upgrading:
 * HelpOnInstalling - how to install the software and supporting files
 * HelpOnConfiguration - how to configure your system
 * HelpOnUpdating - how to update an existing MoinMoin installation
 * HelpOnUpdatingPython - how to move to a more recent version of Python
 * HelpOnSpellCheck - how to configure and maintain the spell checking option
 * HelpOnThemes - how to change the appearance of your wiki
 * HelpOnLanguages - how Moin``Moin uses different languages
